title: George Street Co-op
description: The George Street Co-op is a natural foods store owned and run by its members, and not for profit. They sell vegetarian foods that have the least amount of processing, additives and toxins, with the greatest nutritional value possible. Anyone may shop at the Co-op and choose from a good selection of fresh organic produce, body care and earth-friendly products, bulk foods, vitamins, herbs, gifts and more. Upstairs is an all veggie cafe and juice bar.
